[CONNECTION ESTABLISHED]

“This is planet Fgurbhlporf, are you here to fix the laser?”

“Yes, I am.”

“Great! We've been waiting.”

“No problem. By the way, there's something I'd like to ask you. Why are there these puzzle like elements on your planets? They don't make this repair job any easier.”

“Yes, they were built by the former Empire during the early stages of the revolution. We don't really know why they are here either… All we know is that there should be some kind of purpose behind them, since the Empire suddenly started putting them everywhere. That and that they are a huge nuisance.”

That sounds really strange… shouldn't the Empire have focused on defeating the uprising?

“Alright, well, I guess I just have to find a way around them. Thanks for the information.”
